Description of Ortheziolamameti tranfagliai new species (Hemiptera, Coccoidea, Ortheziidae) from IndiaAbstract This paper describes a new Ortheziolamameti species from the Oriental region (India), namely Ortheziolamameti tranfagliai Konczn√© Benedicty, sp. n. The examined material was extracted from forest litter from India, using Berlese funnels. With this new species the genus Ortheziolamameti now includes six species. An identification key and distribution map are provided.